[**2024 The 8th International Conference on Agricultural and Food Science** (8th ICAFS 2024)](https://icafs.apaset.edu.kg/2024/) will be held in Istanbul, Turkey during October 28-30, 2024\. 
The ICAFS conference website: [https://icafs.apaset.edu.kg/2024/](https://icafs.apaset.edu.kg/2024) 
**Organizers**: 
ICAFS2024 is organized by Asia-Pacific Association of Science Engineering and Technology, coorganized by Dokuz Eyl√ºl University Faculty of Veterinary Medicine, in cooperation with Romania Research Institute for Agricultural Economics and Rural Development, and multiple academic affiliations. 
**Topics**: 
The development of modern agriculture and food science has become inextricably linked to the available science and technology. Therefore, ICAFS2024 has been designed to provide an innovative and comprehensive overview of agricultural and food science and technology. A focus will be given on: 
 \- 1\. Biochemistry and Molecular Biology; 
 \- 2\. Food Chemistry and Engineering; 
 \- 3\. Environmental Science and Engineering; 
 \- 4\. Agronomy, agriculture and plant biotechnology; 
 \- 5\. Animal biotechnology, veterinary, and livestock science; 
 \- 6\. Sensing and Signal Processing, Modeling and Computation; 
 \- 7\. Related Science, Technology and Applications. 
 We look forward to having you join us for this in-person event, for more details about registration please visit at ICAFS2024 registration page. Please also bring this notice to the attention of any of your colleagues who may be interested in participating in the conference. 
 Best regards 
